{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 14,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 451.754,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.161,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then,",
      "verse": "14:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 1.341,
      "end": 4.685,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that if the Gentiles shall listen to the Lamb of God",
      "verse": "14:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 4.865,
      "end": 8.116,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in that day that he shall manifest himself to them",
      "verse": "14:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 8.296,
      "end": 9.364,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in word,",
      "verse": "14:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 9.544,
      "end": 11.077,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also in power,",
      "verse": "14:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 11.257,
      "end": 12.557,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in very deed,",
      "verse": "14:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 12.737,
      "end": 15.338,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the taking away of their stumbling blocks\u2014",
      "verse": "14:1",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 16.018,
      "end": 19.501,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And harden not their hearts against the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "14:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 19.681,
      "end": 22.839,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be numbered among the seed of your father;",
      "verse": "14:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 23.019,
      "end": 26.223,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, they shall be numbered among the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "14:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 26.403,
      "end": 29.886,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall be a blessed people upon the promised land forever;",
      "verse": "14:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 30.066,
      "end": 33.27,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be no more brought down into captivity;",
      "verse": "14:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 33.45,
      "end": 36.469,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the house of Israel shall no more be confused.",
      "verse": "14:2",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 37.149,
      "end": 40.4,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And that great pit, which has been dug for them",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 40.58,
      "end": 43.32,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by that great and abominable church,",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 43.5,
      "end": 46.797,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which was founded by the devil and his children,",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 46.977,
      "end": 50.321,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he might lead away the souls of men down to hell\u2014",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 50.501,
      "end": 53.009,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, that great pit which has been dug",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 53.189,
      "end": 55.093,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the destruction of men",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 55.273,
      "end": 57.734,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be filled by those who dug it,",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 57.914,
      "end": 59.957,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to their utter destruction,",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 60.137,
      "end": 61.762,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saith the Lamb of God;",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 61.942,
      "end": 64.032,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "not the destruction of the soul,",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 64.212,
      "end": 67.788,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "except the casting of it into that hell which has no end.",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 68.468,
      "end": 72.183,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, this is according to the captivity of the devil,",
      "verse": "14:4",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 72.363,
      "end": 75.01,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also according to the justice of God,",
      "verse": "14:4",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 75.19,
      "end": 79.695,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon all those who will work wickedness and wicked practice before him.",
      "verse": "14:4",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 80.375,
      "end": 82.79,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the angel spoke to me, Nephi, saying:",
      "verse": "14:5",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 82.97,
      "end": 85.524,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "You have seen that if the Gentiles repent",
      "verse": "14:5",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 85.704,
      "end": 87.562,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it shall be well with them;",
      "verse": "14:5",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 87.742,
      "end": 90.9,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and you also knowest concerning the covenants of the Lord",
      "verse": "14:5",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 91.08,
      "end": 92.845,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "14:5",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 93.025,
      "end": 96.926,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and you also have heard that whoso repents not must perish.",
      "verse": "14:5",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 97.606,
      "end": 99.835,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Therefore, woe be to the Gentiles",
      "verse": "14:6",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 100.015,
      "end": 103.591,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if it so be that they harden their hearts against the Lamb of God.",
      "verse": "14:6",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 104.271,
      "end": 106.872,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For the time comes, saith the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 107.052,
      "end": 111.417,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I will work a great and a marvelous work among the children of men;",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 111.597,
      "end": 113.873,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a work which shall be everlasting,",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 114.053,
      "end": 116.607,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "either on the one hand or on the other\u2014",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 116.787,
      "end": 120.409,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "either to the convincing of them to peace and life eternal,",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 120.589,
      "end": 124.397,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or to the deliverance of them to the hardness of their hearts",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 124.577,
      "end": 126.713,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the blindness of their minds",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 126.893,
      "end": 130.051,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to their being brought down into captivity,",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 130.231,
      "end": 131.949,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also into destruction,",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 132.129,
      "end": 134.497,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both temporally and spiritually,",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 134.677,
      "end": 137.324,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the captivity of the devil,",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 137.504,
      "end": 139.176,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of which I have spoken.",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 139.856,
      "end": 142.828,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then when the angel had spoken these words, he said to me:",
      "verse": "14:8",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 143.008,
      "end": 146.863,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Do you remember the covenants of the Father to the house of Israel?",
      "verse": "14:8",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 147.043,
      "end": 148.436,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I said to him,",
      "verse": "14:8",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 148.616,
      "end": 149.545,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed.",
      "verse": "14:8",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 150.225,
      "end": 151.85,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then he said to me:",
      "verse": "14:9",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 152.03,
      "end": 153.005,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look,",
      "verse": "14:9",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 153.185,
      "end": 156.064,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold that great and abominable church,",
      "verse": "14:9",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 156.244,
      "end": 158.891,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the mother of wicked practices,",
      "verse": "14:9",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 159.071,
      "end": 160.836,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose founder is the devil.",
      "verse": "14:9",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 161.516,
      "end": 162.909,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said to me:",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 163.089,
      "end": 165.272,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold there are only two churches;",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 165.452,
      "end": 168.146,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the one is the church of the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 168.326,
      "end": 170.602,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the other is the church of the devil;",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 170.782,
      "end": 174.404,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, whoso belongs not to the church of the Lamb of God",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 174.584,
      "end": 176.627,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "belongs to that great church,",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 176.807,
      "end": 179.408,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the mother of wicked practices;",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 179.588,
      "end": 182.142,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and she is the whore of all the earth.",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 182.822,
      "end": 184.912,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I looked",
      "verse": "14:11",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 185.092,
      "end": 187.46,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and saw the whore of all the earth,",
      "verse": "14:11",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 187.64,
      "end": 190.008,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and she sat upon many waters;",
      "verse": "14:11",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 190.188,
      "end": 193.16,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and she had dominion over all the earth,",
      "verse": "14:11",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 193.34,
      "end": 196.869,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "among all nations, kindreds, tongues, and people.",
      "verse": "14:11",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 197.549,
      "end": 200.103,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw the church of the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 200.283,
      "end": 202.512,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and its numbers were few,",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 202.692,
      "end": 208.172,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the wickedness and wicked practices of the whore who sat upon many waters;",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 208.352,
      "end": 210.767,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but, I saw that the church of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 210.947,
      "end": 212.99,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who were the saints of God,",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 213.17,
      "end": 215.771,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "were also upon all the face of the earth;",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 215.951,
      "end": 219.434,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their dominions upon the face of the earth were small,",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 219.614,
      "end": 222.772,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the wickedness of the great whore whom I saw.",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 223.452,
      "end": 227.307,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw that the great mother of wicked practices",
      "verse": "14:13",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 227.487,
      "end": 231.527,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "gathered together multitudes upon the face of all the earth,",
      "verse": "14:13",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 231.707,
      "end": 233.936,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "among all the nations of the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "14:13",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 234.116,
      "end": 236.67,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to fight against the Lamb of God.",
      "verse": "14:13",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 237.35,
      "end": 240.926,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I, Nephi, saw the power of the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "14:14",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 241.106,
      "end": 244.914,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it descended upon the saints of the church of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "14:14",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 245.094,
      "end": 247.741,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and upon the covenant people of the Lord,",
      "verse": "14:14",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 247.921,
      "end": 251.543,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who were scattered upon all the face of the earth;",
      "verse": "14:14",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 251.723,
      "end": 253.766,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were armed with righteousness",
      "verse": "14:14",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 253.946,
      "end": 256.314,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and with the power of God in great glory.",
      "verse": "14:14",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 256.994,
      "end": 259.316,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw that the wrath of God",
      "verse": "14:15",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 259.496,
      "end": 263.258,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "was poured out upon that great and abominable church,",
      "verse": "14:15",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 263.438,
      "end": 267.246,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so much so that there were wars and rumors of wars",
      "verse": "14:15",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 267.426,
      "end": 270.445,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "among all the nations and kindreds of the earth.",
      "verse": "14:15",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 271.125,
      "end": 274.747,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And as there began to be wars and rumors of wars",
      "verse": "14:16",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 274.927,
      "end": 279.107,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "among all the nations which belonged to the mother of wicked practices,",
      "verse": "14:16",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 279.287,
      "end": 281.005,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the angel spoke to me, saying:",
      "verse": "14:16",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 281.185,
      "end": 284.668,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, the wrath of God is upon the mother of harlots;",
      "verse": "14:16",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 284.848,
      "end": 286.845,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold, you see all these things\u2014",
      "verse": "14:16",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 287.525,
      "end": 290.544,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And when the day comes that the wrath of God",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 290.724,
      "end": 293.278,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "is poured out upon the mother of harlots,",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 293.458,
      "end": 297.684,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the great and abominable church of all the earth,",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 297.864,
      "end": 299.861,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose founder is the devil,",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 300.041,
      "end": 301.759,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then, at that day,",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 301.939,
      "end": 304.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the work of the Father shall commence,",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 304.395,
      "end": 308.11,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in preparing the way for the fulfilling of his covenants,",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 308.29,
      "end": 312.655,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he has made to his people who are of the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 313.335,
      "end": 315.518,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the angel spoke to me, saying:",
      "verse": "14:18",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 315.698,
      "end": 316.534,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look!",
      "verse": "14:18",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 317.214,
      "end": 319.072,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked and saw a man,",
      "verse": "14:19",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 319.252,
      "end": 321.481,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he was dressed in a white robe.",
      "verse": "14:19",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 322.161,
      "end": 323.786,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said to me:",
      "verse": "14:20",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 323.966,
      "end": 326.845,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold one of the twelve apostles of the Lamb.",
      "verse": "14:20",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 327.525,
      "end": 329.661,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, he shall see and write",
      "verse": "14:21",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 329.841,
      "end": 331.791,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the remainder of these things;",
      "verse": "14:21",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 331.971,
      "end": 334.618,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, and also many things which have been.",
      "verse": "14:21",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 335.298,
      "end": 338.409,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he shall also write concerning the end of the world.",
      "verse": "14:22",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 339.089,
      "end": 342.572,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, the things which he shall write are just and true;",
      "verse": "14:23",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 342.752,
      "end": 345.028,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold they are written in the book",
      "verse": "14:23",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 345.208,
      "end": 348.505,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which you saw proceeding out of the mouth of the Jew;",
      "verse": "14:23",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 348.685,
      "end": 352.447,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and at the time they proceeded out of the mouth of the Jew,",
      "verse": "14:23",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 352.627,
      "end": 356.249,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or, at the time the book proceeded out of the mouth of the Jew,",
      "verse": "14:23",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 356.429,
      "end": 359.866,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the things which were written were plain and pure,",
      "verse": "14:23",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 360.046,
      "end": 363.343,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and most precious and easy to the understanding of all men.",
      "verse": "14:23",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 364.023,
      "end": 365.277,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold,",
      "verse": "14:24",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 365.457,
      "end": 368.708,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the things which this apostle of the Lamb shall write",
      "verse": "14:24",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 368.888,
      "end": 371.303,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are many things which you have seen;",
      "verse": "14:24",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 371.483,
      "end": 373.991,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold, the remainder shall you see.",
      "verse": "14:24",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 374.671,
      "end": 379.036,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But the things which you shall see after this you shall not write;",
      "verse": "14:25",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 379.216,
      "end": 382.699,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the Lord God has ordained the apostle of the Lamb of God",
      "verse": "14:25",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 382.879,
      "end": 384.458,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he should write them.",
      "verse": "14:25",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 385.138,
      "end": 387.367,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also others who have been,",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 387.547,
      "end": 389.823,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to them has he shown all things,",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 390.003,
      "end": 391.768,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they have written them;",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 391.948,
      "end": 393.759,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they are sealed up",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 393.939,
      "end": 396.029,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to come forth in their purity,",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 396.209,
      "end": 398.717,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the truth which is in the Lamb,",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 398.897,
      "end": 401.405,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the own due time of the Lord,",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 401.585,
      "end": 403.071,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 403.751,
      "end": 406.445,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, heard and bear record,",
      "verse": "14:27",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 406.625,
      "end": 409.783,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the name of the apostle of the Lamb was John,",
      "verse": "14:27",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 409.963,
      "end": 412.331,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the word of the angel.",
      "verse": "14:27",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 413.011,
      "end": 416.401,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, I, Nephi, am forbidden that I should write",
      "verse": "14:28",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 416.581,
      "end": 420.018,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the remainder of the things which I saw and heard;",
      "verse": "14:28",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 420.198,
      "end": 423.309,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so the things which I have written is enough for me;",
      "verse": "14:28",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 423.489,
      "end": 427.576,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I have written but a small part of the things which I saw.",
      "verse": "14:28",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 428.256,
      "end": 429.881,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I bear record",
      "verse": "14:29",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 430.061,
      "end": 433.08,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I saw the things which my father saw,",
      "verse": "14:29",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 433.26,
      "end": 436.0,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the angel of the Lord made them known to me.",
      "verse": "14:29",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 436.68,
      "end": 440.813,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I make an end of speaking concerning the things which I saw",
      "verse": "14:30",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 440.993,
      "end": 443.269,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "while I was carried away in the Spirit;",
      "verse": "14:30",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 443.449,
      "end": 446.143,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and if all the things which I saw are not written,",
      "verse": "14:30",
      "lineIndex": 152
    },
    {
      "start": 446.323,
      "end": 448.552,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the things which I have written are true.",
      "verse": "14:30",
      "lineIndex": 153
    },
    {
      "start": 448.732,
      "end": 450.079,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thus it is.",
      "verse": "14:30",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 450.259,
      "end": 451.095,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "14:30",
      "lineIndex": 155
    }
  ]
}